---
title: Vietnamese-Style Pork & Veggie Tacos with Aioli & Crispy Shallots
description: Sweet and savoury pork is the star of this crowd-pleasing meal. Easy and satisfying, these tacos come together in a snap, with
lots of veggies for everyone to build their own and join in the fun!
